  16 Jun 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> files/lesspipe.sh-r2,
  -less-382-r1.ebuild:
  Fix a quoting issue in lesspipe.sh-r2 and add a trap to prevent 'Broken pipe'
  messages. Thanks to Glen in bug 38854

*less-382-r1 (15 Jun 2004)

  15 Jun 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> +files/lesspipe.sh-r2,
